    <item>
      <title>德国商业银行在抵御裕信银行攻击时更新战略的关键要素</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/key-elements-commerzbanks-strategy-update-it-fends-off-unicredit-2025-02-13/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国商业银行周四表示，将裁员 3,900 人，并公布了更雄心勃勃的财务目标，这是该银行战略改革的一部分，旨在阻止裕信银行为德国和意大利银行之间的合并提供资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/key-elements-commerzbanks-strategy-update-it-fends-off-unicredit-2025-02-13/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 06:17:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>武伊契奇称即使美联储放慢利率步伐，欧洲央行仍可继续降息</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/ecb-can-keep-cutting-rates-even-if-fed-takes-it-slow-vujcic-says-2025-02-13/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克罗地亚政策制定者鲍里斯·武伊契奇表示，即使美联储行动放缓，欧洲央行今年也可能再降息三次，但政策放松的前提是基础通胀率必须快速下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/ecb-can-keep-cutting-rates-even-if-fed-takes-it-slow-vujcic-says-2025-02-13/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 06:11:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国因卖空行为罚款摩根大通、摩根士丹利、野村和瑞银</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/south-korea-fines-jpmorgan-nomura-ubs-morgan-stanley-short-selling-breaches-2025-02-13/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国金融监督局官员周四表示，韩国市场监管机构已对摩根大通、摩根士丹利、野村和瑞银因违反国内股市卖空规则处以罚款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/south-korea-fines-jpmorgan-nomura-ubs-morgan-stanley-short-selling-breaches-2025-02-13/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 05:11:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>独家：摩根大通首席执行官戴蒙嘲讽办公室工作阻力，要求提高效率</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/jpmorgan-ceo-dimon-derides-in-office-work-pushback-demands-efficiency-2025-02-13/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据路透社审阅的一份录音显示，摩根大通首席执行官杰米戴蒙在周三举行的一次热闹的全体员工会议上驳斥了部分员工要求放宽该银行五天复工政策的呼吁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/jpmorgan-ceo-dimon-derides-in-office-work-pushback-demands-efficiency-2025-02-13/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 01:42:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行管委纳格尔对模糊的“中性”利率目标和美国关税损害表示担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/ecb-should-cut-rates-gradually-not-target-neutral-nagel-argues-2025-02-12/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国央行行长纳格尔周三表示，欧洲央行应逐步放松政策，而不是以难以定义的“中性”利率为目标，但如果全球贸易战爆发，欧洲央行需要做好为欧洲而战的准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/ecb-should-cut-rates-gradually-not-target-neutral-nagel-argues-2025-02-12/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 17:33:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>消息人士称，摩根大通开始计划在 2025 年裁员</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/jpmorgan-chase-begins-layoffs-with-more-planned-barrons-reports-2025-02-12/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位知情人士周三对路透社表示，摩根大通上周已开始通知部分员工裁员，这是该行今年计划的几次裁员之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/jpmorgan-chase-begins-layoffs-with-more-planned-barrons-reports-2025-02-12/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 16:34:39 GMT</pubDate>
